4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive course in Data Science and Machine Learning specifically designed for beginners, with no prior experience required. Over a span of 16 weeks, students meet three times a week in small classes of up to 12 participants. The curriculum covers essential skills such as Python, SQL, and data visualization tools. Participants will engage in hands-on projects, mastering algorithms for predictive modeling and machine learning techniques. Graduates receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop